3module ActiveSupport
4 module Cache
5 # A cache store implementation which doesn't actually store anything. Useful in
6 # development and test environments where you don't want caching turned on but
7 # need to go through the caching interface.
8 #
9 # This cache does implement the local cache strategy, so values will actually
10 # be cached inside blocks that utilize this strategy. See
11 # ActiveSupport::Cache::Strategy::LocalCache for more details.
12 class NullStore < Store
13 prepend Strategy::LocalCache
